      "description": "Beautiful, renovated family home on a prime corner STEPS TO DOUGLAS PARK. Main route offers convenience while the home is remarkably quiet from dbl glazed windows &amp; lush front hedging for privacy. Large E facing windows fill the interior w/natural light. Main floor offers formal living &amp; dining rooms plus separate den ideal for home office,or playroom. A bright kitchen w/ eating area &amp; NS mnt views. Upstairs,3 spacious bdrms, one w/a generous balcony perfect for morning coffee watching the sunrise. Lower level has exceptionally high ceilings w/a bright 2 bdrm suite w/separate entry, large windows &amp; gas fp. Great accommodation for extended family or mortgage helper. 2 oversized single garages for vehicles &amp; storage, or the flexibility to create a workshop. Emily Carr &amp; Eric Hamber catchment ",
